Step 4 - Download

Download report

- Interested user with the Power BI report shared by Alumni can download the report

To do this:

1. Go to the Shared with me menu 

- Click on Shared with me menu 

- Select and click the report from the Alumni folder but not Dashboard Usage Metrics (monitoring activities)

2. The user can go to the file menu and click and then see all the options listed

- Click on the download

The report will be downloaded with .pbix format 

- The down load will go to the downloads folder of the user machine





Download report from Power BI Service to Power BI Desktop

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/service-export-to-pbix
